00:04:11.180 --> 00:04:12.340
ready

00:04:12.900 --> 00:04:15.960
now start decorating, for that you can use deco paper

00:04:16.180 --> 00:04:20.180
and cut squares 1 cm less than the squares of the box

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:22.470
in this case of 5 cm

00:04:28.460 --> 00:04:31.250
you can also use ribbon and figures of the perforator

00:04:39.770 --> 00:04:41.520
fill the box with whatever you want to give

00:04:43.500 --> 00:04:45.440
